Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想变成尸鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:06.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你这么体贴小律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尸鬼的帮凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:21.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智寿子还是这么精神 年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:28.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟年轻没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是经常帮家里搬米 习惯搬重物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是大婶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:36.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:40.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智寿子都算大婶的话那我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还算是大婶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:43.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:47.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这个还在动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:02.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:06.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:10.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 茶叶柱立起来了
