Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.06,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.13,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.13,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什么
