Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.68,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}当一切造访
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:07.01,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:07.01,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(235,330)}終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:07.01,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要将死亡叹作恐怖吗
